  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>You will develop knowledge and understanding of constructed textiles, dyed textiles and printed textiles – ultimately creating and constructing a successful outcome design.</p>
<p>You will also have opportunities to get involved in fashion shows and exhibitions.</p>]]></mainContent>
